  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK893">
<l>keṭalvēṇṭiṟ kēḷātu ceyka vaṭalvēṇṭi</l>
<l>ṉāṟṟupa varka ṇiḻukku</l>            
          </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a person desires ruin, let him not listen to the righteous dictates of law, but commit crimes against those who are able to slay (other sovereigns).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
